Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这边不够
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸灯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就帮你拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.59,0:01:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花  你那边忙好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过难得来那么多客人  真是可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  在许愿板上要写什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？ 我还没决定好…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  好好想一想啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似还很灵验的哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想啊野心什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.41,0:02:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名我呀～总而言之就是好想留学～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在外国学一些关于旅馆的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有还有～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一位娇小的女性神明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了报答用纸灯照亮她的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而把他们的愿望带到天上去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.01,0:02:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到汤乃鹭后  我希望自己能够闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后每天都过得手忙脚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我觉得自己已经喜欢上工作和喜翠庄了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的梦想是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人数如此众多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到晚餐的筹备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能够尽可能地削减花在早餐上的劳力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐不要送到客房  而是用自助餐的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我想会有客人喜欢在房间里慢慢吃早饭的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没法子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房已经忙不过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人退房后打扫房间也很难办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子她们还要去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再使用每个房间都由专人负责的形式了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还在揽客吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吩咐过你们不要再接待客人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是其他旅馆揽得更多都没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看你们这么多人不停叫唤着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还叫没事么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是要降低服务的质量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要努力下一番工夫来克服眼前的困境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是自助餐  料理还是料理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝没有半点想偷工减料的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服务也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管没有专门负责的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在其他所有方面上  我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  随你们喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过相对地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有雪洞祭  你们得用以往的方式给我好好干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…这些是许愿板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…在上面写上各自的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂在纸灯上…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是做那些的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我拿一块
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉有点不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样希望喜翠庄可以继续开下去但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你罢手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再站在老板娘那一边了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是站哪一边什么的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有能回的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能回的…地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我就没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟雪洞祭什么的根本没有关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.55,0:05:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有…我的梦想在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为…本以为你跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还高兴过那么一阵…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在喜翠庄工作的所有人都是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜… 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在这里住上一阵  没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.67,0:06:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但睡那地方没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天实在是忙不过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想多出一点力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在努力…大家虽然都在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不觉得大家有在雪愿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  与其要睡那边的话  不如到我床上…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  快点睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天四点就要起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}小民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四…四点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在都已经过了十二点了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得小菜也在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却连聊天都不能聊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太沉闷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子…实在有点…讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可没工夫悠悠哉哉地散步哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要帮忙的是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你在大家面前说句话的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站在老板娘那边也只会被大家孤立
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是站哪一边的问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想让喜翠庄重振旗鼓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你不是平时的你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是平时的你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用别人说  早就自顾自地把事情搅得一团糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后硬是带来一种乐观向上的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.87,0:08:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而那样的你却…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变的不是喜翠庄  而是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先在大厅里接待客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认他们的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不要忘了问早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  要添粥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  这个煮菜相当讲究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到自助餐里都能吃到那么棒的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用符合时节的食材
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合上独到的精湛手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都说好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐全都变成自助式的了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是的  就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是以前那种悠闲的气氛更好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啦  这样也挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  果然还是间隔大些比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是再往左边点好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  我打算用当地画家的作品把这里布置成画廊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也可以带来一笔可观的收入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变的  喜翠庄会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花你也…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄会变…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是变了  我最喜欢的喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有雪洞祭…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想让阿孝看看的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么  想让朋友看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不再接待客人了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这间房可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让他看看喜翠庄是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样  让他作为你的朋友留宿在这里便好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老  老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身体啊情绪啊什么的还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为老板娘怎么会那么好心…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你重要的朋友对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是非常感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤来  喂——  民子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  彻先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.52,0:10:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到民子公主的睡相了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个彻是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…呐  小民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}别来跟我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在跟你怄气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为绪花你站在老板娘那一边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤来同学她喜欢绪花的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是不那么想…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤底熬得怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就去看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子  把蔬菜给洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些结束之后就去处理鸭子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都如彻先生所说  能做一位厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…  我之所以执着于这里的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.20,0:11:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为有彻先生在  有莲先生在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有大家在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.26,0:11:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种奇怪的东西怎么能拿得出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}我说  莲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碗配菜怎么还没准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人已经开始抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然要换掉配菜 麻烦的可是我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 莲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}你居然把错推到我头上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么怎么  两位到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}你来厨房抱怨之前  就不能想想自己能干些什么么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是争吵的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}你说什么！别把厨房的问题推给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻必须齐心合力…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}看你像块豆腐一样禁不住事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}你懂什么这叫敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯洁的心灵才是最珍贵的你不懂么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要保护喜翠庄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄…现在是重要关头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请走好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  告个别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为这是个能让客人高兴的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家一起努力  连我也一起感觉到很幸福的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  现在喜翠庄却不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都只在意老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是已经知道老板娘真正的心意了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我最喜欢的喜翠庄  是老板娘一手创造的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想勉强别人去附和她的梦想么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘是不会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她自己是能够奔跑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有自己的梦想  不能奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要能够去追随那些有着梦想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这便是他们的梦想了  这样的人也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要正式开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定许愿板上要写什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那喜翠庄的人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给他们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…因为一直手忙脚乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶～我说  绪花你是不是被无视了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名我去帮你催催
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 结名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}不等你～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}我说结名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到祭典了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游客们从各地赶来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人是从东京来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…因为打扮的这么艳丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爷  好痛  好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.07,0:15:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs19}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊  在这重要关头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去向协会求救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们家也去问过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是雪洞祭前夕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有人手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪洞祭前早餐和服务都要按以往的方式去做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是和老板娘约好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去和老板娘认错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个做法的话一定还有办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要继续干
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  给我老实待着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还怎么能老实待着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就输给老板娘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输给…老板娘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作要分输赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:15:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样太奇怪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起让客人开心  赢过老板娘更重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赢的话喜翠庄就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在的喜翠庄不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我喜欢的喜翠庄还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才找到能释放自我的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在场的各位都是同一个心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是同一个心情  却又不知为何背道而驰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄已经是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  虚幻之城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说一下大家的心声…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来代替吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.94,0:17:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做女服务员的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能弥补巴的缺口了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.36,0:17:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换换心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天两夜  大人一位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐现在预约已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不是说这个的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  和绪花一个房间好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我住的话  工作我也能帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里那么大声的争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明这么忙前台却一个人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  真的要帮忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缘…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗是我们的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让老板娘…还让姐姐来帮忙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱有个人感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:18:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要保护喜翠庄吗  Anything
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.38,0:18:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  到了雪洞祭当天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子  现在就去月之间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  忙不过来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让姐姐去？但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷  月之间是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:18:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴衣的尺寸  把M换成L
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷  今天我是女服务员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好发出指示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,称呼错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该是老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 请多关照了  翠女士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子  渍菜拼盘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下装饰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧烤好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是波之间 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子  这边交给我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这脚打扫还是没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴会场那边拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alright…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 停
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是鹤之间  鹤之间…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点摇摇晃晃而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是休息一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅馆生意客人最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.84,0:20:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己只能排第二第三
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呀  我却对此乐在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回到你的工作岗位上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雕刻就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤之间还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.02,0:20:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲先生  天妇罗炸好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤之间的我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在这里努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.21,0:20:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}慢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和老板娘一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}明白了  寿之间是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:20:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.10,0:21:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都用完餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了大家  我们渡过了难关
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.44,0:21:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:21:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间松懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家该出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.55,0:22:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是去参加雪洞祭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你  最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}如果能被原谅的话  希望能再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}我终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的…
